                "title": "What I See, What I Do, What It's Actually Like",
                "header_size": "h2"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "blog_s5_stories_intro",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Not every post needs to be useful. Some things are just worth writing down. Personal projects I'm working on, places I have visited, things I have noticed, and the occasional behind-the-scenes look at what goes into a shoot without identifying the people in it. No names, no locations that would compromise anyone's privacy.</p>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
